Hello,

Our company Scrap Trading 24, located in Tunisia, presents its services to individuals and companies in the field of non-ferrous metal waste collection.
Taking into account your activity, we have identified a collaboration of our companies allowing the development of our respective companies.
Indeed, you are a specialist in recycling non-ferrous metals and we are specialized in the recovery of these types.
We collect waste throughout Tunisia from professionals and individuals.
The treatment and trading of non-ferrous metal waste form the heart of our business.
Scrap Trading 24 controls all the activities of the recycling chain, from the collection of end-of-life materials to the marketing of new secondary raw materials in Tunisia and throughout the world.
Upstream, we offer you optimal collection and recovery solutions and support the environmental management of your activity.
We work in our network only with certified suppliers and controlled scrap to guarantee the quality of the factory for further processing.
Thanks to our network, we have better access to the qualities of the scrap metal and we can provide you with materials that exactly match your needs.
We have a sorting service which controls the quality of the scrap.
For a departure we offer 21 tons of copper waste .
Pending a hopefully favorable response please accept, our best regards.
